products.title: Avoca Atria Pink Electric Roller Blind
products.description: The avoca atria electric roller blind will improve style and light control in any space. The handy electric functionality enables you to easily dress hard to reach windows and brings an element of modern luxury and convenience to your lifestyle. This fabric design feature subtle, on-trend tones of dusky pink and grey in a simple design of pretty botanicals. Product id: db-erbx2006 fabric colour: pink material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: electric control battery powered energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes avoca atria pink electric roller blind in pink.
